Who is Gräfik for?

Gräfik is built for companies that rely on shift-based work and where scheduling is essential. Examples include:

  • Healthcare (hospitals, nursing homes)
  • Restaurants & cafés
  • Construction & industrial companies
  • Retail & service businesses
  • Call centers and so on...
